title: Week 12 recap
itunes:title: Week 12 recap
description:
A room filled with heroes - Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling, Marc Sessler, and Dan Hanzus – break down all the action in Week 12, including the Broncos handing the Patriots their first loss of the season in an overtime thriller, and the Seahawks making things interesting in the AFC Wildcard race with a win over the Steelers.
